structured.title: Shepard Navigates Noveria‚Äôs Corporate Intrigue
structured.overview:
This transcript captures a gameplay-style narrative on Noveria involving Commander Shepard, Gianna Parasini, Administrator Anoleis, Captain Maiko Matsuo, and various corporate figures. Shepard‚Äôs arrival triggers a tense weapons confrontation with port security until Parasini confirms Spectre credentials and allows the party through. Parasini explains Noveria‚Äôs strict, profit‚Äëdriven corporate privacy and heavy security, and hints that the planet hosts cutting‚Äëedge (and possibly dubious) research beyond Citadel jurisdiction.

Shepard seeks information on Matriarch Benezia, who is confirmed to have passed through the port and travelled to the remote Peak 15 research complex with asari commando escorts and sealed cargo, all under the authority of Saren as a major Binary Helix investor. Anoleis stonewalls Shepard, citing corporate autonomy, a blizzard grounding shuttles, and closed surface access, refusing direct clearance to Peak 15 and emphasizing that project leads, not politicians, set safety and research protocols.

Parasini quietly advises Shepard that brute force won‚Äôt work on Noveria‚Äôs bureaucracy and suggests talking to Lorik Keene, a Synthetic Insights manager whose office Anoleis has shut down over alleged corruption. Meanwhile, an asari representative from the Aramali City Council recruits Shepard for a covert corporate espionage task: pose as a buyer with Binary Helix salesman Rafael Vargas at the hotel bar, keep him talking, and deploy a hacking device to breach his personal network. Shepard negotiates pricing on genetic enhancement packages, steers the conversation toward Binary Helix‚Äôs activities on Noveria, and successfully completes the hack, then leverages that success to upsell the payment from 500 to 750 credits.

Later, Shepard meets Lorik Keene, who offers a garage pass and credits in exchange for recovering incriminating evidence on Anoleis from the sealed Synthetic Insights office. Keene warns that Anoleis has enlisted Port Hanshan security to search his offices and that violence may be unavoidable. When confronted by security inside the office, Shepard uses Keene‚Äôs pass for entry and aggressively orders the guards to leave, escalating the standoff and underscoring the ruthless, high‚Äëstakes corporate environment on Noveria, where legal authority is fluid and driven by executive board interests rather than galactic law.

## Docking bay confrontation  
- Security blocks entry; demands credentials and disarmament  
- Spectre status confirmed; weapons allowed by Captain Matsuo  
- Parasini apologizes, notes strict corporate security and secrecy  

## Learning about Benezia and Noveria  
- Planet outside Citadel law; board defines ‚Äúlaw‚Äù  
- Matriarch Benezia passed through, went to Peak 15  
- She arrived with asari commandos, heavy sealed cargo  

## Meeting Anoleis and travel restriction  
- Administrator Anoleis only cooperates per executive board  
- Confirms Benezia is Saren‚Äôs executor, on Binary Helix business  
- Peak 15 access denied: private facility, blizzard, shuttles grounded  

## Parasini‚Äôs hint and Keane lead  
- Parasini says you can‚Äôt brute-force corporate bureaucracy  
- Points you to Lorik Keane at the hotel bar  
- Keane holds another pass to leave port  

## Binary Helix data theft for Parasini  
- Parasini targets BH salesman Rafael Vargas at hotel bar  
- You pose as buyer; plant cracking device during talks  
- Device works; Parasini pays 750 credits after negotiation  

## Deal with Lorik Keane  
- Keane‚Äôs office closed; accused of bribing Anoleis  
- He has evidence of Anoleis‚Äô corruption in his office  
- Offers garage pass and credits if you retrieve it  

## Office break-in and security clash  
- Use Keane‚Äôs pass to enter Synthetic Insights office  
- Han Shan security blocks entry, citing ongoing investigation  
- You threaten them to leave or face combat  

## Next steps  
- Recover corruption evidence from Keane‚Äôs office  
- Decide how to use evidence: help Keane, Parasini, or neither  
- Use garage pass to reach surface and ultimately Peak 15
